{"tid":892820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖少年考低分被罵　竟用刑事課堂知識殺媽媽","createTime":"2018-11-07T07:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T19:47:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3ed012657fdec0a3b1946756a4981edd96a0e626","tid":892820,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T07:11:45.000Z","msg":"美國佛羅里達州一名15歲少年拉莫斯(Gregory Ramos)，因為一門課業考試拿了低分的D評鑑，被媽媽克麗文吉(Gail Cleavenger)責罵。但拉莫斯竟然一怒之下殺了媽媽，還利用從刑事司法課學來的知識，企圖妨礙警方辦案，讓警方和社會大眾都相當震驚。<br />\n據美國《紐約郵報》報導，拉莫斯近日的成績單上，有一門課拿到D等，算是低分。媽媽克麗文吉得知後，念了拉莫斯幾句，還告訴了正在西雅圖出差的拉莫斯父親。就在本月1日，母子兩人為了成績的事大吵一架，就在深夜時分，拉莫斯潛入克麗文吉的房中，把媽媽叫醒後當場勒斃。就在2日，拉莫斯報警，但他稱家裡一度遭竊賊闖入，而且媽媽失蹤不見。<br />\n但警方進一步追查發現，案情並不單純，而且已被拉莫斯動了手腳。警方發現，拉莫斯勒斃母親後，叫來兩名同夥，把母親的屍體埋到附近教堂的火坑裡。之後3人返回拉莫斯住處，故意將現場布置成遭竊盜入侵的狀態。警方更發現，拉莫斯相當「學以致用」，他曾在學校裡上過刑事司法相關課程，還是警局義工，而他利用這些知識企圖掩蓋罪行，譬如把漂白劑倒進埋屍的洞內，以掩蓋氣味。他還給警方提供假線索，一度聲稱他的母親虐待他。<br />\n警長奇特伍德(Mike Chitwood)就表示，拉莫斯是他遇過反社會者中，能排進前3名的恐怖少年。而且拉莫斯被逮後完全沒有悔意，更對自己的殺母手法感到「自豪」。目前警方除了逮捕拉莫斯，也逮捕了兩名同夥，全案仍持續審理調查中。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181107/640_5ffc4ec2f14f2d29de80c6efd3b0f50f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181107%2F640_5ffc4ec2f14f2d29de80c6efd3b0f50f.jpg&h=88394395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖少年拉莫斯考低分被罵，竟用刑事課堂知識殺媽媽。翻自《紐約郵報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181107/640_eabf12741785fdf51ceb17efd0617890.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181107%2F640_eabf12741785fdf51ceb17efd0617890.jpg&h=bfe3767a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n媽媽克麗文吉。翻自《紐約郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181107/1461780/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181107%2F1461780%2F&d=jVDurkuBn2F%2F4seFalLcD26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=b526c643\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181107%2F1461780%2F&h=bb1b384d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181107/1461780/</a>"},{"pid":"83bdb0e105c5a7515610b540aa611f897783519d","tid":892820,"uid":191352,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T07:12:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe5c01dc1e981cb789b8812d2f76d3fbc49f7124","tid":892820,"uid":185142,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T07:13:51.000Z","msg":"媽媽快d強奸我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd69a8eb22c191d22bbf60956a995cedaf7afa89","tid":892820,"uid":38492,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T07:14:26.000Z","msg":"拉莫斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804c3340b5809c07fb2969669bb6d934cb25e5b0","tid":892820,"uid":125760,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T07:14:52.000Z","msg":"火化又點解會有埋屍既洞？ 1999"},{"pid":"981cb5b6200360c9a1593c327a2493e690c367cd","tid":892820,"uid":27146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T07:15:56.000Z","msg":"怪唔知得考得咁低分啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a77199ac31212d889ecbca496ba9c43d5314657","tid":892820,"uid":55903,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fe5c01dc1e981cb789b8812d2f76d3fbc49f7124","tid":892820,"uid":185142,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T07:13:51.000Z","msg":"媽媽快d強奸我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T07:16:34.000Z","msg":"今晚佢會黎搵你"},{"pid":"90d7be3faa68b8991ae8dd8f76feb6d3f68a2054","tid":892820,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd69a8eb22c191d22bbf60956a995cedaf7afa89","tid":892820,"uid":38492,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T07:14:26.000Z","msg":"拉莫斯<img src=\"/assets/f